---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Projects — AIBolt Labs" description="Open-source software and interface systems from AIBolt Labs.">
  <section class="page-hero"><div class="shell"><div class="eyebrow">Project catalogue</div><h1 class="page-title">A small collection,<br />maintained with care.</h1><p class="lead">Projects enter this catalogue when the source is public, the boundaries are documented, and someone else can use the work without inheriting the lab itself.</p></div></section>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="shell">
      <div class="rule-heading">Published</div>
      <div class="catalogue">
        <article class="catalogue-row"><span>01</span><div><h3>DYNT</h3><p>Formation and Kinetic interface engines.</p></div><p>Framework-neutral core packages with optional React and Web Component lifecycle adapters.</p><a href="/dynt">Project record →</a></article>
        <article class="catalogue-row"><span>01A</span><div><h3>@dynt/formation</h3><p>Reversible, line-led interface construction.</p></div><p>Nine geometry profiles, viewport acquisition, observation, and explicit lifecycle phases.</p><a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/@dynt/formation">npm package ↗</a></article>
        <article class="catalogue-row"><span>01B</span><div><h3>@dynt/kinetic</h3><p>Contact-led physical interface response.</p></div><p>Directional tilt, waves, four cell renderers, content response, and operational budgets.</p><a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/@dynt/kinetic">npm package ↗</a></article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section-tight"><div class="shell open-callout"><div><div class="eyebrow">Source and stewardship</div><h2>Public to use. Deliberate to change.</h2><p>Source is open for inspection and use. Proposed changes are reviewed by the maintainers so the project can evolve without losing its contracts.</p></div><a class="button" href="https://github.com/aibolt">Browse GitHub ↗</a></div></section>
</BaseLayout>
